Arconti Financial Advisors (AFA) is a full service, fee-only financial planning and investment management firm in Danbury, Connecticut.
People from all walks of life turn to AFA for an in-depth perspective on their finances; or simply for a second opinion on a specific financial matter. That’s because we are a different type of financial services firm. We offer needs-based service that allow our clients to select only the services – as much or as little – as makes sense to them. As your planning partner, we assist you in designing strategies and solutions to meet your unique needs.
Arconti Financial Advisors is completely independent. We are not affiliated with any mutual fund company, brokerage firm, or insurance company. We have no products to sell, no quotas to meet and no commissions or sales incentives that might influence any recommendations. At AFA, there is no account value or net worth minimums, as we believe professional financial advice should be available to anyone who seeks it.
Whether you choose to engage AFA on a one-time, hourly/project basis, or wish to begin an on-going investment management relationship, you can expect expert guidance with only one purpose in mind; your financial success.
Please explore our website and then call (203) 778-4100 or email info@ArcontiFinancial.com to inquire about a no-cost, no-obligation Get Acquainted meeting.
